\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Your name is Frederick Hanrahan, 77 Edge Lane Drive, you're }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128  and you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128  in 1927 - 1926 - you were born in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4598440\charrsid5861128 1902}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598440\charrsid5861128 don\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128  you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You were born in Liverpool - how many years did you lived in the house in which you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many years did I live in house which was born? Well I suppose - whether I was born there or not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Which house did you live in the longest before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh that was Stewart Place. I think I was born in Stewart place and I was there 'til I was twenty-four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many brothers and sisters did you have? Ernie was the eldest wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Our Else was the eldest. And our Les, Ernie - myself and Stan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I don't know how old he was when I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old was he when he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was sixty-eight when he died and I was twenty-four. So that gives him forty-four. He would be forty four when I was - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He came from Ireland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was a tram driver wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was a tram driver - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he have any other job before or after that do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 The Army. Joined the Army. The Army - the Inniskillens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And then he came to Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was just - finished his time, twelve years in India and then - then came here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was on that job until he died wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes. Well - cleaning - he was cleaner for - well, he'd retired hadn't he. He was doing a bit of cleaning in the sheds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Only when the strike was on - - the tramway strike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Go back into that as well then. She died when she was sixty-two. I would be - what - thirty - I'd be about thirty-seven then wouldn't I.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 So she'd be twenty-five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well she always - always brought up in Liverpool as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did she have any jobs before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, she never worked - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many room were there in the house at Stewart Place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Stewart Place - three bedrooms. And - what they used to call a parlour and kitchen. And back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 So more or less six rooms weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Six roomed house, yes. No bathroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No other relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother pay anybody to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. But she had two aunts - who lived two or three doors away. Who used to look after - our Ern and me - we practically lived there see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But that was just to help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Your mother didn't go out to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh done at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well me mother used to make - dressmaking. What - what - you know, little trousers and things like that. And - the aunts used to do quite a lot of sewing - patching. Making t
hings like that. Or - and mend. In those days you know there was a lot of women who used to make trousers and things and we used to go to a house not far away where she used to make trousers and things for us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were the clothes you bought new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598440\charrsid5861128  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, clothes, always new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And were the shoes always new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 They were new too, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Repairs or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
No. Of course in those days the - the landlord used to do the decorating you know. He used to decorate the rooms - well, later on as I was older I did the decorating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he dress or undress or bath you or read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, he never - he never took any part like that with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or look after you when she was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not as I - I can't remember. See I wasn't - actually with the paren
ts all that time. When I was young I was with the aunts more so than - although they were only two or three doors away. But I slept there and had most of my meals there. But apart - like me father never used to do any - he had his allotment but - as far a
s house was concerned he didn't do any work there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have any jobs you had to carry out regularly at home to help your aunts or your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not really. We would perhaps clean knives and forks, you know, on the old - you know
 the board they used to have. But I wouldn't say we had to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You had no jobs you had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you do anything after you left school for these people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 At home you mean? Well I did a bit of decorating then. And helped my father on his allotment. Watering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your brothers have any set jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the older children help the younger with things they found difficult like dressing or eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well - not as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the younger children help the older in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, wouldn't say we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother or your aunts put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I can't remember really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can you remember what age you were before you put yourself to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you share the bedroom or bed with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, at the aunts we had our own beds. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In the same room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No they had three rooms - two aunts used to sleep together at first see. Then we - had - there was the other - other two rooms you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well we used to bath downstairs. When we were young, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How often did you have a bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Once a week - every Saturday. Every Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When did you put clean clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Put clean clothes on every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In the kitchen. What we called the kitchen in those day
s but there was a back kitchen apart from that. Yes, but the cooker was in the kitchen where we had the meals. That's where we lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, we always ate there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you aunt - where did she cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well they - no, they didn't - they had the gas ring but they also had - the oven on the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When you were going to school when was breakfast eaten? Did you all eat together-your brother and yourself and your aunts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, we'd all have it together, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Nobody went out before you went to school did they? In your mother's house your dad would have gone out first wouldn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh well he used to go out at four o'clock in the mornings sometimes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But in your case it would be different wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes. There wouldn't be nobody going out. When I went to school there wouldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you generally have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Now that's a problem. Some morning we would have porridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you have for midday meals - did you come home from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I came home from school - we always had a good hot dinner when we came home from school then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you have for evening meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well the evening meal would probably be bread and jam or - something like that I should think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 On Sunday did you have anything special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well we'd have a good breakfast on Sunday - bacon, egg. Good dinner. And a good tea as well on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What would you call a good tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well you'd have some meat or something and - jelly or blancmange, things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother or father or your aunt bake their own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 The aunts used to bake their own bread and bake them for me mother as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they make their own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Made their own jam, yes, all things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they make wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or medicines for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Oh we used to have brimstone and treacle, yes. Yes. And liq
uorice powder. Once - once a week we had the liquorice powder. Every Saturday night that was. You had your head combed as well with the fine tooth comb.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well he didn't grow his own fruit, he grew his own vegetables and all that kind of stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No, well I don't think there were very many in those days were there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you keep any livestock for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh we had some meat of some description every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was it tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no. Fresh meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever get some extra meat such as rabbit from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, he always had more - he always had good food. He'd have bacon and egg every morning. Good hot meat dinner.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 As far as - I know we never bothered much about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh we had to have a bit of everything that was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was your parents or your aunts attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I don't think we ever did leave any uneaten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask someone to pass it to yo
u or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, you just took it when you - when you wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, I'd say so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well I don't remember being taught to hold it but I reckon we did hold it - we used to hold it the right way. I don't remember being taught how to hold it though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Could you bring toys or a book to the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, they didn't like you reading when you were having your meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well we used to leave when we'd finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have to ask if you could leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I don't - I don't remember when we were very young whether we did or not but we didn't afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, in those - in that case we did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you always have the same place at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How was the meal served - who served it - one of the aunts was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Oh yes, yes. Oh it was always served - properly like because they'd - they'd been cooks and they'd been in service. And everything was done as it should be done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What order was it served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no, it was all served out at the same time and you all started at the same time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was it served in a tureen or out of the pot it was cooked in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 It'd be put onto your plate right out of the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did the younger brothers and sisters sit before they could feed themselves and who fed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was only our Stan was younger than me. And of course I wasn't there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was your mother and easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Providing you did as you were told.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If you had any worried could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well wouldn't say we did do. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was your father an easy person to get on with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh very easy. Never bothered with us at all. As long as we - didn't get into any trouble he never interfered with us at all,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I don't know how they expected us to but we - we behaved - we didn't give any cheek or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I don't think so. We used to all get on all right together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well - it - it wasn't a matter of what they hoped you'd grow up to be, it was - there was always a shortage of - I wouldn't say there was a shortage but there was never too much money and they could always do with a
 bit more so as soon as you - you came fourteen - they weren't very interested in whether you - where you worked so long as you had a job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents bring you up to consider certain things in life important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh honesty, yes, honesty. That was one thing me father was always keen on, you - you had to be honest like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did they think of swearing - was there any swearing in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, there wasn't. No. Even me father didn't in the house. He may have done outside, he didn't in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If you did something your parents did not like what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh I don't know - I remember chipping in once when I was with me mother out somewhere, 
she was talking to somebody like and she said, oh I got - got across the ear hole you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was that the only time you were punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That's the only time I remember over that particular thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh I didn't - I never thought anything of it at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Would you say you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well me mother must have played the most important part becaus
e she brought - I wouldn't say me father - had anything at all to do with us, like he didn't really bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no different at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you receive any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Have anything special to eat or have a guest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, used to have the proper Christmas - we used to have the Christmas dinner - oh and me mother 
would play the piano in the parlour. Yes. And we'd be in there. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Your mother used to play the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or - on other occasions like we would all go to the aunts and have our tea - but not me father, he never used to - he didn't bother w
ith anything social at all. Well his job was - he worked all hours and he worked all sometimes Christmas Day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was your mother the only one to play the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Me sister played.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 As I say on occasions like that, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother or father ever play any games with you or your aunts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh there was plenty of books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, weren't a lot of newspapers - the Echo and one Sunday paper that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 They never used to buy maga - not - none of these woman's books what they have now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes. Me father would read - 
he'd read anything. Even the books we used - you know, when we used to come in with the Union Jack, the Magnet and things like - he would read all those. Yes. Or - or our library books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they ever read aloud to one another or to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember a funeral in the family before 1918?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Before 1918? 1918. No, can't say as I do before 1918. 1918. No, no. No, I don't remember - not before 1918 - me father was the first one. That was - oh that was what - twenty \endash  twenty eight it would be - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. We never had any relatives anyway. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you ever taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If we wanted clothes and things that's the shopping we would do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You never went for the Saturday shopping - the household shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I used to have to do a lot of shopping - messages and things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever go out just with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember any outings with your parents - on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Oh yes, we - well I wouldn't say it was Bank Holidays well perhaps when he was on his holidays - New Brighton or Southport. West Kirby. Just for days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well before I started work - Saturdays - that goes up to where I was ten - well we weren't allowed out. We weren't allowed out to play in the street, we were kept in the back yard with - the two aunts never let us out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Every Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well Sunday we used to go to Sunday school and church in the mornings see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you spend Sundays then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well we used to go to Sunday school - always the Church Lads Brigade, used to
 have church parade in the morning perhaps, Sunday school in the afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have different clothes on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, we always had Sunday suit and shoes and things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you play games on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents or your aunts attend a place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, used to go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Which one was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 St Anne\rquote s.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How often did they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh I think me mother used to 
go every Sunday night very near. And me aunts would perhaps go to communication - I wouldn't say every Sunday but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But your dad never went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, 'course he was a Catholic but he never went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, oh I used to attend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did you generally go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Hail Wood. That's the only one I remember - Hail Wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What other social activities organised by the church did you take part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well as I told you I was in the Church Lads Brigade, we used to have a - a meeting once a week. Drilling and things like that. Then I was in the Kings Messengers which was another night.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Making - things to sell for the missionaries and things. These - weaving and stuff like - raffia stuff you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you belong to a choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the church or chapel run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Band of Hope, yes, they did have a Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you a member of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. I don't think so, I don't think there was any other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, I suppose we were. Yes we would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. He didn't really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You don't know what his views were then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh he - I know he - he used to 
be Liberal. He used to be a Liberal. That - that was - when it was an election on well that was the only time he would -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Have you any idea why he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no idea. He went Labour afterwards. 'Course he was Liberal before the Labour party started. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was your mother's attitude?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I don't think she really bothered tell you the truth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember your father voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He always voted - he always used his vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You don't know who he voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I should say he voted Liberal 'til the Labour party was formed and then he would be Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their e
mployers - do you know if your father felt himself under this kind of pressure to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
No, I don't because he worked for the Corporation like. If he worked for an individual employer he probably wouldn't - think he would have the same - same as they used to do in the cotton and things like that didn't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was your father a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember him working for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I'd say me mother's work was never finished, she was always working. And me father - he had the allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Church perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I - she never - I - she may have been in the - the mothers meetings and things like that, I wouldn't - I wouldn't be sure about that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Very little enjoyment. She used to go to the pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well that's a difficult question because - he could b
e any time. If he was on early start at four o'clock in the morning he would probably finish about five or six but if he were on late he could come in after midnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You never knew when he was coming in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No. Well you would know - according to his shift.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many evenings a week would he spend at home of those or at the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
When he was off early he would spend most - an hour or two on the allotment every night. But in the winter months well he wouldn't go out - he would just sit by the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he go to any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
He - he used to take an occasional drink but that was mainly - mostly of a weekend if he was off on a Sunday but otherwise - while he was coming from the allotment he might.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother go with him at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, she didn't go in the pub much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs - a boot club, sick club or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
He belonged to the sick club. They used to - one in Green Lane, I forget what they used to call it. Used to be about sixpence a week - tontine kind of thing. And then if you were off sick you got about - ten or twelve shillings a week I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And a funeral club was the usual insurance wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was - that would be your insurance policy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother or father belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When we were young we got on very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was there one you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I'd say our Earn more than any of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Because he was nearly your age wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He was - nearer my age - eighteen months difference you know. And then he was with me at the aunts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 As a child who did you play with, your brothers, sisters or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well mostly me brothers. Or me brother I'd say.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did you play - in the yard, garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well as we got a bit older we used play out in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When you were very young before leaving school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well we played very little out there at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You wouldn't be allowed to go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You play cric
ket when you have two gable ends or - running round the block. Really o, they used to call it. Kick the can. Peggy. Buttons. Cherry wags. Yes. Buttons where you used to put the button on the tramlines so it would flatten it out. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well, no, there were certain ones they didn't like you playing with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I should think - probably thought they were dirty or they - weren't good enough or something like that I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well, no, they didn't like you going in dirty or with your clothes torn or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you belong to a youth organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Only this Church Lads Brigade which I suppose you'd call that a youth organisation wouldn't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school? Did you keep any pets, collect anything, do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Can't say as I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Just swimming. Baths.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who did you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh with - boys from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was more or less part of the lessons wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And of a night as well like sometimes. 'Cos we used to - later on I used to go with you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not really, I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Before you started work did you go to the theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Before I was ten you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes. Did you go to any theatres, concerts, music-halls, cinemas while you were still at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, I remember-going to different things - go up the Olympia one time to - see circus things. But that would be only occasional like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who took you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well I've been with the aunts, I've been with me mother. But they were only special occasions those - something special on for children probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever go to the cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Not before I was ten I wouldn't say I went to cinemas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes - well - I think so on - when - penny on a pass.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was the pass people used to display in their shop windows wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That's right - yes. You had a pass you only paid a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I used to get about a pan - a penny a week of me father. That was all we would get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you spend that on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Sweets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you get that penny a week regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family? Your two aunts helped look after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, well that was all. 'Cos there wasn't - there was no other family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well I don't remember her ever being confined to bed, I've known her when she hasn't been well but she still had to carry on with the work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You wouldn't remember when Stan was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You were only a baby yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby - your mother had her two aunts didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, well that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How much did she see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh saw them every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In their house or in yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well in any - more - more often or not in their house - the aunts house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents have any friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I wouldn't say father had any friends but - the only - he knew the chaps on - the fellows who he worked with on the allotments.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And he saw them on the allotments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 On the allotments and when he was working with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother have friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well mainly neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did she see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh she wouldn't see - only when they were out because - we didn't have anybody running in the house - in and out the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You told me your father saw his friends on the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, that was the only place he - or in the street. Not - none came into the house. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Friends were never invited into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You don't remember any friends or your mother's or father's being invited in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No, not really I don't - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did friends ever call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, wouldn't say -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well they wouldn't come in - they'd have to talk at the door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Would they be invited in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got out together with their friends and neighbours? You said they very seldom went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, they wouldn't - no, they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to one and some to another group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In what way? 
Well there were some people better off than others. But I never thought of them as being better than - apart from the money I didn't think they were any better than anybody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Could you tell me what the different ones were - how many groups do you reckon there were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well there were some worse off than what we were. And there were some better off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Which class would you say you belonged to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Between those two you mean? Well we would be in the middle wouldn't we.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What sort of people belonged to the same class or group as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well - ordinary working class people - 'cos some jobs that you thought some jobs then were better than others like we don't know but you wouldn't think a fellow who emptied the bins then, y
ou wouldn't think he was as good as your father because he had a better job. I mean, anybody worked in an office you would think they were a bit above you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You don't think that situation holds today?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, certainly not - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What sort of people belonged to the other classes or groups - you have mentioned that - the men who emptied the bins and ordinary job.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Sweeping the streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Are there any other groups you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh well shopkeepers, you always thought they were better 
off than what - the ordinary working man was. Schoolteachers. Even - even insurance man, you thought he was a bit - a bit higher classed than what you were yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No I don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were you ever taught to touch your cap or show respect in some way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well you were taught that in school - you had to do - you were really taught to do that in school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who did you have to do that to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well - perhaps - anybody - a schoolteacher - people from the church or even some of the - people in the - neighbours in the street.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any one you called Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I didn't call anybody Madam. But you'd call most people Sir in those days didn't you if they were older than you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember anyone showing respect to your parents in this way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No I don't - can't say as I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In the area where you lived who was considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I
n that particular area? Well we used to look to the teachers didn't we. And policemen - you did have you did have respect for the policeman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you consider they were the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I don't - I don't know we looked upon it then as being the most important but we were mainly frightened of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you come into contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Not really, no, not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can you tell me why you considered they were important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well - even if you were playing sometimes you
 thought you were doing wrong and if they came round they'd be after you. Playing football and cricket in the street like you -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What about the shopkeepers - who did they associate with in that area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well in that particular area the children wou
ld play with us. And - they were small shops which you didn't look upon them - really as - when I'm talking about shopkeepers really I'm talking about the grocers - the big - large grocers and - things like that. Not the small shops. And they were only sm
all shops round our particular area.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever come into contact with teachers outside the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. We didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 So you wouldn't know who they mixed with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What about employers? Did you know any employers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What sort of people would you say went to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well the most - the majority of people who went to church were - neighbours. And the of course was others - better off who went to the church as well. There was people who - owned businesses 
round there, small businesses and that. But actually they were better off than what we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who went to the chapel then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What do you call the chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 The Methodist groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I don't know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 There was no distinction actually was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where you lived did all the people in your particular group have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh there were different groups. Some - I wouldn't say anybody in our particular street w
as any better off than what we were but some were worse off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well they wouldn't have as much - although we didn't have a lot of money they wouldn't have as much. Or else they were - either weren't working or they had a poor job as - as I say like. Or they'd have more children. Or some drank more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or they had a better job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And they drank more they could still be worse off. Or their families could be worse off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, they had one or two - you always found the odd one or two who thought they were a bit better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Any idea why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I think maybe because they had been better off and they'd come down. There was one particular family in our street who
 - who - I - they were - the mother was more of a gentlewoman say than the majority would be and I think they'd been better off and I think they'd come down and - although they would - they would speak to you and all that. Nobody ever went in their house 
- well as I say, nobody went in ours either. Yes, but - they - and their children were never allowed out either. Or if they were they only played with themselves.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were some families thought of as rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember a distinction of this kind between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I can't say as I can remember anything like that in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes or groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class or group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was it possible at that time to move from one class or group to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well if you - say 1 if you
 moved your house to a better neighbourhood well then you would be wouldn't you, and it was possible to do that in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Can you remember anybody who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I can't say as I can - but I remember people coming into ours which was a six roomed house which was better than a four roomed house.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember anybody being referred to as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well because - well in one case in particular he was a real ge
ntleman, he - he - he was - he had a good job, in an office, something like that - always well dressed but he would always raise his hat to the people - the likes of the aunts or me mother. Oh yes. And do you know who that would be? Know Hutchie that used
 to be the - his brother. Proper gentleman he was - yes. And his - his sister was a proper - what you would call a gentlewoman too. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember seeing a policeman round where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, often used to see a policeman, he used to always walk the beat then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you think of him? When you were naughty did your mother ever say I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, but me father always impressed on us never get into any trouble with the police like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you think the police in those days treated the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well I think they treated the people very well. The - you were more in contact with them, you knew them and they knew you. Far better than it is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Was your home rented?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, he come round every week for the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you think about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh the landlord himself when he - when we were young, he - the chap who owned the house used to come round for
 the rent himself like. And he was - he was a - he was a - a nice man and - used to do the decorating as I say, used to do the decorating.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you think about this at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well when you're young you don't think about it do you - take these things for granted. Well you always knew they wasn't - that your mother was doing without so; that you got wasn't she. Although I didn't see that so much because living with the aunts.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What difference did it make to the family if your father was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well he was only on strike once - I don't remember it. Must have been before I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever get any help from the Guardians or the Parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When you first started what time in the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And what time did you come home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Four. Came home for dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Twelve to half past one would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Church of England - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How far was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 About a quarter of an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who took you at first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I couldn't remember. Probably of the other - one of the other - aunts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did you have your midday meal then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I used to come home and have it in the aunts, yes. Used to have a proper midday meal. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Meat and potato?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, that would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I didn't mind school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I thought the teachers were all right too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the teachers emphasise certain things in life as important - such as manners, tidiness, punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Which do you think they thought was the most important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Cleanliness - tidiness - manners.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 If you did something the teachers didn't like what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well you'd probably get the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they punish the girls the same as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I don't know because ours wasn't a mixed school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you get the cane for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I think if you were behind with some of your work in school you would get the cane those days, if I remember rightly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 When they got the report they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they ever visit the school to meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Although me mother knew the teachers although she didn't meet 'em - well it was when they took us in the first place like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the other children at school come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Majority - some a bit better some - a little worse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Gangs of boys and that you mean? No, I don't think there was in our school. Not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, don't think so. Playing in the school yard and things like that? No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That's the only school you went to isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well I never thought of it an that particular time - I don't think you did think about it. You're thing was - your main thing was to get out and earn some money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you attend any part time education afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I didn't when I was about seventeen or eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But not at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I would have done - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You were telling me people were rather upset with you when you went to a factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, because they thought I should have gone - I could have done better. In thos
e it was in an office - well there's a chap up the green-groce I worked for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And who else - the headmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 The headmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well there's a greengrocer who lived near us. And - me brother worked for him - for him as well see, he worked there. He used to work Friday nights - Tuesday, Friday night and Saturday I think he used to work. And then they wan
ted another boy to - for - he had a brother who was in - he had a son who was in the same business see. So me brother worked for his son and he wanted somebody to go round with him on Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That's how you got the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That's how I got that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What did you have to do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Well it was a greengrocers. And I used to - Saturday morning - I started Saturday mornings - used to get one and three pence a - one and three pence for that. I used to - go round certain roads, get the o
rders, come back. Make them up and then take them out. That was on Saturday - that would perhaps bring twelve or one o'clock and then afterwards I used to go out with him in the cart. And I would be out to eleven or twelve o'clock of a Saturday night.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You only got one and three pence for the whole lot?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 One and three pence for the Saturday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But you didn't work any other time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. The only thing is that - I think I was a bit older - when I was coming home from school one day along 
Prescot Road and there was a chap there had a secondhand shop - old junk and stuff - and he called me over. And he said, would you like to do something for me? And - that was to go and - after I'd had my dinner go to his house, which wasn't far from us - 
s
ay ten minutes from home - pick his dinner up in a basin and take it to the shop. And I used to have to go down the cellar, fill his kettle with water and bring it up. And I did that for - five days a week and used to get half a crown a week for that. And
 I did that 'til I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You got half a crown off him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
I was never short of money from when I was ten. That was my half crown that was. And of course I used to get more from the greengrocer after because I used to do Tuesday night and Frid
ay night and Saturday and get half a crown for that. But that half crown, I got nothing out of that because that went away - for clothes. Same as me one and three pence used to go away - it never went in the house, it was put in a box and when I wanted ne
w suits or boots or anything that money was there. And our Ern - both myself and our Ern bought our own clothes from when we were ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you think you were fairly paid or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 It was an average wage then, yes. I thought I was well paid with the half crown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And you used to spend that on yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was mine that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You didn't save that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. Oh I did save - I used to be in penny bank. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But it didn't go to your clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get on with the other people who you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Oh, got on very well with them. And I used to get me dinner there as well you know. Oh aye - smashing dinner. And see - and - used to give me jam bread, like when I went out in the cart say from one o'cl
ock, she'd give me about four, oh, big chunks of jam bread. And I got a bit fed up with this jam bread. And - I used to leave it in the cart after - I couldn't eat - I didn't eat it and he asked me one day like didn't I like jam bread. So - he gave me tup
pence then and I used to go and buy a cake. Of course used to get loads of fruit and vegetables going home in the Saturday night off him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You liked the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes. And Sunday morning we used to take the horses to the field. Yes, we - we'd get - pu
t a sack on the horses back and ride it to the field. And bring it home on the Monday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you do any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 First full time job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Oh I left school on - I left school on the Friday, went up to this factory - do you want to know the name of the factory? Crawfords. Crawfords biscuits. Me brother wor
ked there and me sister worked there so I thought - thought I might as well go there and I went up on the Monday morning. I was engaged and started at dinnertime. Unloading tins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Fourteen. I was just fourteen that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was your fourteenth birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 That was me fourteenth birthday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I think it was seven thirty 'til - six would it be then - wouldn't it. I think seven thirty 'til six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have a half day off on a Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you work on Sunday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Not - not in that early stages, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have holidays with pay in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 There was no holidays. I used to take a holiday 'cos I used to go to camp with the Church Lads Brigade. But you didn't get paid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What were the wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 My wage I think was twelve and six a week when I started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you think it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I suppose I did in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Gave it all to me mother, used to get sixpence back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Sixpence back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you get on with the other people at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh - all right with the other people at work, very well, yes. Work in gangs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What exactly did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Used to unload tins. Empty tins from the - the vans when they came in and apart from your twelve and six you were on bonus. Would we call it bonus in those days? Yes, used to get - for every thousand tins that your gang unloaded - three in a gan
g - you got so much per thousand, I can't remember how much it was now but it used to take the money up quite a lot. And - was - I was really never short of money, from when I was ten I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Would it be possible that you wouldn't get sufficient work and you wouldn't get the basic rate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh no, you got your basic rate - in those days you got your basic rate.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did your employer treat you - or the boss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I used to get on all right with the bosses myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You liked him did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He treated you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you like or dislike the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I did like it yes, I didn't mind it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did the job alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No I can't say as I thought much about school afterwards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How many jobs have you done since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I've only had the one job. One - the one firm, not the same job only worked for to one firm in different jobs I've worked in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Will you give me the jobs you've done there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I 
went - I worked in the warehouse where we used to load the full tins of biscuits in the vans and - I've worked - in the jobbers - jobbing, putting slates on the roof or - repairs and that kind of thing. I've worked up at the recreation ground - rolling th
e
 tennis courts - moving - jobs like that. Then back to the factory. Into the stores where we used to receive the flour, sugar and all that kind of stuff. And from there - setting up the - the ingredients ready for going down into the mixers. And then from
 
that onto the mixers where mixing the - the ingredients, making the dough. What was me next job? Oh and then I - I went in the packing room - training - watch - how to pack biscuits and - see them coming out of the ovens and back to the stores again as a 
c
harge hand. And from there to assistant foreman - in the stores. And I finished up in charge of - stores - where the - on the ovens baking the biscuits and the packing room as well which I - I'd - me training had been taught me. And I finished up as that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Would you have preferred another type of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well when you look back I suppose you would but I was quite content with - I had quite a variety of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You never served an apprenticeship but you had certain training periods for some of the jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, oh yes, I never -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever go to a training school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, I've been to Clayton Manor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well it's where they have training courses for - mainly dealing with people, not so much the work as - dea
ling with people where you - you had lectures from all different kinds of people - trade union officials and - these tutors - how to handle people and how to solve problems and one thing and another. 'Cos majority - most of the people have never had these
 kind of work themselves so how they could teach you how to do it I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you belong to a trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I used to belong to a trade union.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you take part in its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. not really. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well in the early days they had different interests. The worker was no - not to be compared with the boss - in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 But you don't think that exists today?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I don't think it does exist today. You're pretty well on the same level - you treat each other as equals now more so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you feel that there were divisions of interests amongst the workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Say some workers getting a better deal than the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
Oh yes. Was always a certain amount of favouritism for some and - some'd get better jobs and you think what you should have had them yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Some people say in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers - did you feel this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 The - no, the only division would be the money, there wasn't - with the actual dealings with the men themselves I wouldn't say there was.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, I don't think so. I've never really thought much about like 'til I went there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No. No. We went out more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Or with your brothers and sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, we had less to do with them then - you didn't bother much with them then, you had your own friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you spend your Sundays any differently - did you still go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
For a short time - not very - not very long. No. I still stayed in the Church Lads Brigade for a while. But not for - I wouldn't say more than two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spa
re time - did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way or did you do different things after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Yes, it probably did. Probably went to - pictures more - or the theatre. Later on when we got they bikes - cycling. Dancing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 You made a lot of new friends during that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 How did you meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Mainly in work. And friends of theirs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you ever bring your friends home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I - I brought them home, yes. When you called for each other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have any special friends at this time - boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh well it'd be boys - wouldn't be girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Where did you go with these boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well pictures or - out walking. Hire a bike. Go to the baths. Hire a bike for say t
hree pence an hour. Well you could - you used to hire the bike - I think it was about three pence an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 I think it was sixpence an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 In those days was it? Sixpence an hour. And you hired a bike for sixpence an hour and perhaps keep it out
 three or four hours and when you took it back you'd just leave it outside the shop. And run, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did your parents know who you were going out with - meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh yes, most times they did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did they expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well they'd ask where you'd been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Did you have to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 No, not really. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Have you any idea when your sister was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What is she - she's seventy-three now. She must have been born about 1896 or seven mustn't she.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was her job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 There wasn't an awful lot of difference between any of us really. She worked in Crawfords.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 What was she doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Oh she was checker - checker in the stock room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 She }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
 a docker didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 She }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 
 a chap on the docks, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Who was the next brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Our Les. Well he worked - he worked at Carwfords.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Any idea when he was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well I would say - our Les is sixty-nine. Our Les would probably be about seventy-one I
 think. So he would be born about 1899 wouldn't he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Which school did he go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well he went to St Anne\rquote s school. He went to Crawfords. And he left Crawfords - went to Blackledges.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 He died before he got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16466707 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128  didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13129044 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 Well then - a
nd he had an accident in Black-ledges - he got his arm under the roller and - and that would be the cause of him going into bad health after and dying see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2830963 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11430278\charrsid5861128 And then Ernie?
