t
he ship to - the dock or whatever it is, anybody wants to sail like, so and that's the way he - quite a lot used to go away to sea that way you know. Jump a ship, aye. Well - jumping a ship really is when you - at the other side. But this is the thing - i
t's the same - jumping onto it instead of jumping off it you see.
