e that you see. And he stuck - he went away to sea for a few years. And then - I don't know whether he left or the ships weren't going but then it was getting a bad period - there was no work. So he joined the Navy. Oh aye, was in the Navy. I don't know h
o
w many years he did there - may have been three or four. And then he went back to sea again. Then he jumped a ship in America then. And he stayed there for quite a few years sailing out of America. Aye on the - the American runs. Then he - he came back he
