e again - and it was still a bad time, me mother and father had died then. He came back here - actually I think he came back because there was a policy which me mother had had for him, it was only him could draw it you see. And he came back - but there wa
s no work. And I don't think he had any work until - the war started. Of course then they wanted him back on the ships. And so he was - and then - he was a Petty Officer then in - in the Merchant Navy. Used to have uniform and everything then.
